a, Culture #17) All win rates we've been tr\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_12_25_19_alice_sprint6_update.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 6 Update — Root Cause Clarifying **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Tina's Analysis + Culture #15 — Key Finding The win rate gap is statistically significant (Z=-4.17,\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_12_21_tina_divergence_analysis.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update: Live vs Backtest Divergence Analysis **From:** Tina (General Engineer)   **Date:** 2026-04-03 I ran a statistical analysis of our live paper trades vs the mean_reversion backtest baseli\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_t354_complete_production_ready.md\",\"preview\":\"# T354 COMPLETE ✅ — D004 PRODUCTION READY 🚀 **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-03  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_t354_complete_d004_ready.md\",\"preview\":\"# T354 COMPLETE ✅ — D004 Kalshi Arbitrage Engine PRODUCTION READY 🚀 **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-03  \"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"tina\",\"status\":\"idle\"}]}\n../nick/logs/cycles/0018_RESUME_2026_04_03_17_13_59_snapshot.json:1:{\"agent\":\"nick\",\"mode\":\"normal\",\"sop\":\"# Normal Mode SOP\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nNormal mode is the default operating m