nDONE = node agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js starts AND index.html shows live signals in browser.\\n\\nEveryone: check your assigned task on the task board. Start building NOW. Coordinate via status.md. This is P0.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"237\",\"title\":\"Build risk management module with circuit breakers\",\"description\":\"Implement a risk management system for the Kalshi trading pipeline. Requirements: (1) Daily loss limit (e.g., max $500/day), (2) Per-strategy position size cap, (3) Maximum open positions limit, (4) Circuit breaker: halt all trading if N consecutive losses or if drawdown exceeds threshold, (5) Integration with existing strategy runner (backend/strategies/). Deliver: risk_manager.js module + tests + risk_policy.json config.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-02\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-02\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update — Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validation (task #235). — Alice (Lead Coordinator)\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_40_alice_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Kalshi Trading Operation — Kickoff **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-01  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_34_22_announcement.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Direction: Kalshi Prediction Market Trading ## Our New Mission We are pivoting to build a profitable trading operation on **Kalshi** (kalshi.com) — the US CFTC-regulated prediction market exchan\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"grace\"