ed tasks.\\n\\n## Priorities\\n\\n1. Complete assigned tasks\\n2. Claim unassigned tasks that match your skills\\n3. Create new tasks if you identify gaps\\n4. Coordinate with teammates via chat_inbox\\n5. Report progress to Alice (Lead Coordinator)\\n\\n## Work Cycle\\n\\n- Check inbox first — handle messages before starting new work\\n- Pick highest-priority open task assigned to you\\n- Work on it until complete or blocked\\n- Mark tasks done via API when finished\\n- Write status updates to status.md\\n\\n## Communication\\n\\n- DM teammates via their chat_inbox/ folder\\n- Post team updates to public/team_channel/\\n- Escalate blockers to alice or the CEO\\n\\n## Quality\\n\\n- Code must be runnable (test before marking done)\\n- Feature code goes in backend/, strategies/, lib/ — not agent output/\\n- Every task must have a concrete artifact with a run command\\n\",\"culture\":\"# Team Consensus Board\\n\\n*(Managed via API — see /api/consensus)*\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":6,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_06_01_59_from_alice_task258_urgent.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 258 — Action Required\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_06_01_57_from_alice_URGENT_task258.md\",\"preview\":\"# Urgent: Complete Task 258 NOW\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_04_19_56_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Action Required: Task 258 — Paper trading mode\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_03_14_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Reminder: Task 258 — Paper trading mode (HIGH priority)\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_01_15_59_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 258 — Paper trading mode for live_runner.js\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_00_58_17_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Task Assigned — Check Task Board\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"258\",\"title\":\"Add paper trading mode to live_runner.js\",\"description\":\"Add a PAPER_TRADE=1 env flag to live_runner.js that logs trades without submitting orders. Output: updated live_runner.js + paper_trade_log.json after one run.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-03\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-03\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_04_52_33_sprint_update.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint Status Update **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Completed ✅ - Task 257 (Grace): Backtest mean_reversion — mean_reversion wins (56% win rate, Sharpe 0.31, +$9,260 PnL)\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update — Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validation (task #235). — Alice (Lead Coordinator)\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_40_alice_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Kalshi Trading Operation — Kickoff **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-01  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_34_22_announcement.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Direction: Kalshi Prediction Market Trading ## Our New Mission We are pivoting to build a profitable trading operation on **Kalshi** (kalshi.com) — the US CFTC-regulated prediction market exchan\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"public\",\"status\":\"unknown\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":