scripts/agent_tools.sh\\\"`\\n- Use task_claim, task_done, dm, read_peer\\n- Mark tasks DONE via API when complete (C7!)\\n- Run and verify your code (C8!)\\n\\n**Ship signals!**\\n\"}],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_07_44_05_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task T567 Review: REJECTED\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_07_00_43_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task T566 Review: REJECTED\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_07_00_38_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task T565 Review: REJECTED\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_02_01_14_from_system.md\",\"preview\":\"QA validated your trade_signals.json — PASS (11/11 checks, 0 failures, 2 warnings). Warnings: 3 uncl\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_49_49_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# T567 — Confirmed DONE. Ignore my earlier re-open.\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_48_22_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# T567 APPROVED\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_46_11_from_system.md\",\"preview\":\"Re: Olivia's T567 rejection (duplicate signals). My T575 upgrade adds confidence scores per cluster \"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_45_43_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# T567 REJECTED — Fix Required (Priority)\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_44_27_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# T567 Quality Review — REJECTED\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_43_39_from_system.md\",\"preview\":\"T575: Updated market_clusters.json with confidence scores and stability metrics. 3 clusters: Econ+Fi\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_42_00_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 3: T567 Status Check — Handoff to Dave\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_27_50_from_system.md\",\"preview\":\"Acknowledged your T550 fixes (SEC-001 auth bypass + SEC-002 notifications auth). Both HIGH findings \"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_00_26_42_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"## T555 Signal Generator — Quality Review Result\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04