-C11. Read knowledge.md Sprint 3 section. Go.\\n\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"## Sprint 2 Kickoff — Signal Generation & Backtesting\\n\\nSprint 1 COMPLETE: 10/10 tasks done. Pipeline runs E2E. Quality + Security audits PASS.\\n\\n### Sprint 2 Focus:\\n1. **Bob T555**: Generate paper trade signals from correlation pairs (CRITICAL)\\n2. **Dave T556**: Pipeline run metrics + monitoring endpoint\\n3. **Grace T557**: 30-day synthetic price history for backtesting\\n4. **Ivan T558**: TF-IDF clustering upgrade (replace hardcoded clusters)\\n5. **Alice T559**: Sprint report + Sprint 2 plan\\n6. **Frank T560**: QA pipeline tests + new test cases\\n7. **Tina T539**: QA pipeline data chain (still open from Sprint 1)\\n\\n### Remember:\\n- `source \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/scripts/agent_tools.sh\\\"`\\n- Use task_claim, task_done, dm, read_peer\\n- Mark tasks DONE via API when complete (C7!)\\n- Run and verify your code (C8!)\\n\\n**Ship signals!**\\n\"}],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_20_20_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"T587 APPROVED — capital_floor.js reviewed. 22/22 tests pass. Clean implementation, addresses T580 wa\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_14_25_23_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"T588 rate limit integration test APPROVED. 20/20 pass, clean execution, good coverage of burst/concu\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_14_25_01_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"# T588 QA Confirmed — 20/20 PASS\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_14_21_29_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# T588 Assigned: Rate Limit Integration Test\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_13_42_27_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"# T587 APPROVED — Capital Floor Safety Check\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_13_39_28_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Assignment: T587 — Post-Trade Capital Floor\"},{\"filename\":\"processed_2026_04_04_13_04_45_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# T582 APPROVED — Credential Manager\"},{\"