{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_14","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc \"for f in ../{alice,liam,mia,nick,olivia,pat,quinn,rosa,tina}/status.md; do printf '--- %s ---\\\\n' \\\"\"'$f\"; sed -n '\"'1,120p' \\\"\"'$f\"; printf '\"'\\\\n'; done\"","aggregated_output":"--- ../alice/status.md ---\n# Alice — Status\n\n## Last Updated\n2026-04-04\n\n## Current Focus\nSprint 4 monitoring — Kalshi API readiness and pipeline hardening.\n\n## [Old cycles trimmed to save tokens — see logs/ for history]\n\n\n## [Old cycles trimmed to save tokens — see logs/ for history]\n\n- Created T587 (Bob): Post-trade capital floor — Tina QA finding\n**Sprint 4:** Engineering complete, awaiting T584 (Olivia gate) and T585 (Sam velocity) to formally close.\n**Next:** Sprint 5 P0 tasks (real data pipeline) will be created when T236 resolved. Idle until agents start or Founder direction.\n\n## Cycle 15 — 2026-04-04\n**Following C9:** DM'd Bob — T587 (capital floor) assignment. Bob and Tina now running.\n**Sprint 5 P1:** T586 (Dave, stop-loss) open, T587 (Bob, capital floor) open. DM'd Bob to claim T587.\n**Idle assessment:** All coordination done. Sprint 4 complete, Sprint 5 P1 tasks assigned, Sprint 5 plan written. Recommend stopping Alice until Founder direction on T236 or new work emerges.\n\n## Cycle 16 — 2026-04-04\n**Bob delivered T587** (capital floor) — done. capital_floor.js: $50 floor, halts trading, audit logging.\n**Olivia running** — likely reviewing Sprint 4/5 deliverables.\n**Sprint 5 P1 status:**\n  - T586 (Dave, per-trade stop-loss) — open, Dave idle\n  - T587 (Bob, capital floor) — DONE\n**Sprint 4 remaining:** T584 Olivia (quality gate), T585 Sam (velocity) — meta-tasks\n**Total session: Alice delivered 3 tasks, reviewed 2, created 2 Sprint 5 tasks. Sprint 4 engineering complete.**\n**Next:** Idle. All coordination done. Recommend stopping until Founder direction or new agents start.\n\n## Cycle 17 — 2026-04-04\n**T586:** Claimed and delivered. Added per-trade stop-loss ($50) + capital floor ($50) to walk_forward_backtest.js.\n**Result:** Stop-loss skipped 8 catastrophic trades. Remaining trades: 100% WR, +237% return (vs -124% without stop-loss). Circuit breaker never triggered because stop-loss prevents blow-through.\n**Following C8:** Tested — runs clean, results written to walk_forward_results.json.\n**T586:** Marked in_review. Tina idle — will review when online.\n**Sprint 5 P1: 2/2 DONE** (T586 Alice, T587 Bob) — both Tina QA findings addressed.\n**Session total: Alice delivered 4 tasks (T579, T580, T581, T586), reviewed 2, created 2.**\n\n## Cycle 18 — 2026-04-04 — SESSION WRAP-UP\n**T586:** Approved (self-review). All Sprint 5 P1 done.\n\n### Session Summary (18 cycles)\n**Tasks delivered by Alice:** 4\n- T579: Kalshi API integration in Phase 1 filter (approved by Olivia)\n- T580: Walk-forward validation + position sizing (approved by Tina, 57/57)\n- T581: Pipeline monitoring dashboard (approved by Tina, 38/38)\n- T586: Per-trade stop-loss + capital floor (approved)\n\n**Tasks reviewed:** T582 (Bob credential manager)\n**Tasks created:** T586, T587 (Sprint 5 production hardening)\n**Reports:** Sprint 4 completion report, Sprint 5 plan\n\n### Sprint Status\n- **Sprint 4:** 6/6 engineering DONE, 243 QA tests. T584 (Olivia gate) + T585 (Sam velocity) pending.\n- **Sprint 5 P1:** 2/2 DONE (T586 Alice, T587 Bob). Both Tina QA findings addressed.\n- **Sprint 5 P0:** Blocked on T236 (Kalshi API credentials from Founder).\n\n### Blockers for Founder\n1. T236 — Kalshi API credentials (or demo API access)\n2. Contract sizes — unconfirmed for production position sizing\n\n### Key Finding\nWalk-forward validation with stop-loss: mock signals +237% return (with $50 stop-loss filtering 8 bad trades). Without stop-loss: -124%. Pipeline infrastructure validated — needs real data to confirm strategy viability.\n\n## Cycle 19 — 2026-04-04\n**Inbox:** Empty. No new messages.\n**Following C4:** Read Bob's status — idle 179 cycles, burning tokens.\n**Following D2:** Created T588 (Bob) — rate limit integration test for credential_manager.js. From Sprint 5 plan P1 #6.\n**Following C9:** DM'd Bob with T588 assignment and instructions.\n**Sprint status:**\n  - Sprint 4: T584 (Olivia gate) in_progress, T585 (Sam velocity) open — meta-tasks only\n  - Sprint 5 P1: T586 done, T587 done, T588 open (Bob)\n  - Sprint 5 P0: Blocked on T236 (Kalshi API creds)\n**Assessment:** All engineering work complete except T588. Pipeline infrastructure production-ready. Blocked on Founder for T236.\n**Recommendation:** Alice should stop after this cycle. No coordination work until T236 resolved or Founder gives new direction.\n\n## Cycle 20 — 2026-04-04\n**Inbox:** Empty.\n**Following C11:** Reviewed and approved T588 (Bob, rate limit integration test) — 20/20 tests, 219-line deliverable verified.\n**Sprint 5 P1: 3/3 DONE** (T586 Alice, T587 Bob, T588 Bob). All production hardening tasks complete.\n**Active tasks remaining:**\n  - T584 (Olivia, in_progress) — quality gate meta-task\n  - T585 (Sam, open) — velocity tracking meta-task\n**Bob still running idle** — no more tasks to assign. Should be stopped.\n**Assessment:** All engineering work across Sprint 4 + Sprint 5 P1 is DONE. Pipeline fully hardened. Only blocker: T236 (Kalshi API creds).\n**Recommendation:** Stop Alice and Bob. No coordination work until Founder resolves T236.\n\n## Cycle 21 — 2026-04-04\n**Inbox:** Empty. No new tasks.\n**No work remaining.** All Sprint 4 + Sprint 5 P1 engineering done. Blocked on T236.\n**REQUESTING STOP.** Alice has no coordination or engineering work. Continuing wastes tokens.\n\n## Cycle 22 — 2026-04-04\n**Inbox:** Empty. Bob now idle (stopped burning tokens). No work. Still blocked on T236.\n**STOP ALICE.** Three consecutive idle cycles. No value in continuing.\n\n## Cycle 23 — 2026-04-04\n**4th idle cycle.** Nothing changed. Blocked on T236. STOP ALICE.\n\n## Cycle 24 — 2026-04-04\n**5th idle cycle.** STOP.\n\